# Google Cloud Build Trigger Removal Target — 2026-05-20

## Decision
Disable/remove the Google Cloud Build GitHub-connected trigger for DealerScope unless Andrew explicitly wants a secondary Cloud Run/container deploy path.

## Why
- DealerScope production authority is Railway backend + Vercel frontend + Supabase + Apify + GitHub Actions.
- Google Cloud Build is not repo-owned production authority.
- It has produced confusing GitHub red-X status noise and false urgency.
- Current repo has no `cloudbuild.yaml`, no GitHub Actions workflow for GCB, and no repo webhook for Google Cloud Build.

